:movie_camera: New Feature: Data Transformation on Multiple Cards

- Cards Created/Modified Automatically
- Add Field from New/Existing Dictionary Lookup
- Add Field with Color in Other Field's Range
- Calculate Min & Max for a Field
- Explain Why Action can't be Applied
- Replace Current Column with New One
